These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, photographer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, house
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, subway
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the mechanic##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | milk     | cola |
| Hobby         | drawing  | card-games       |
| Job           | photographer   | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | spy   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | reggae     |
| Sport         | basketball | handball      |
| Transport     | subway       | train           |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice
There 2 different types of food: potato, banana
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, freelancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, scientific
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, australian
2 different pets are kept: mouse, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, roller
1. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating banana##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is on the left of the writer##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice         | almond-milk       |
| Food          | potato        | banana |
| Job           | freelancer | writer    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | action  |
| Nationality   | australian        | colombian       |
| Pet           | dog            | mouse        |
| Transport     | roller            | train       |

