2. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the photographer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
5. the photographer is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
