.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, house
2 different pets are kept: rat, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, scooter
1. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | cola    | hot-chocolate   |
| Hobby         | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | crime     |
| Music-Genre   | house        | jazz        |
| Pet           | rat        | snake |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | basketball |
| Transport     | scooter         | taxi       |

