2. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the german is the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
6. the engineer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | security-guard    | engineer  |
